# This project needs no secrets to build or run — all tournament data is
# committed in src/data.ts, and the one data-refresh script
# (scripts/fetch-worldcup26.ts) uses the free, no-auth worldcup26.ir API.
#
# DISABLE_HMR (optional): set to "true" to turn off Vite hot-module reload
# and use polling-based file watching instead (useful in some sandboxes).
# DISABLE_HMR="true"
#
# VITE_UNSPLASH_ACCESS_KEY (optional): a free Unsplash "Access Key" — register
# an app at https://unsplash.com/oauth/applications. When set, tournament pages
# show a champion hero photo fetched from the Unsplash API (free tier: 50
# requests/hour). Without it, the champion section renders its flag-led layout.
# VITE_UNSPLASH_ACCESS_KEY="your-unsplash-access-key"
